    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is equally impressive, showing no meaningful wear on the seats, dashboard, or carpeting; everything looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with all mechanical systems functioning exactly as intended. The tires have excellent tread remaining, all electronics and features operate perfectly, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional used vehicle that will require no immediate investment in repairs or cosmetic work.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
